<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.box1{
				width: 100px;
				height: 100px;
				background: red;
				float: left;
			}
			.box2{
				float: right;
				width: 100px;
				height: 120px;
				background: blue;
			}
			.box3{
				clear: both;
				width: 100%;
				height: 300px;
				background: gold;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h3>ps:使用了浮动属性的元素会脱离文档流</h3>
		<div class="box1"></div>
		<div class="box2"></div>
		<div class="box3"></div>
	</body>
</html>
